My name is Stephanie Zimmer
Senior Research Statistician at RTI international. RTI is an independent, research institute that provides research and technical services to government and commercial clients. Statistics is at the core of RTI. Gertrude Cox established the Statistics Research Division at RTI in 1958
My role includes working on large surveys - sampling design, weighting, overseeing data production
My day-to-day includes lots of management-ish stuff and meetings but I still code quite a bit
My stats group works on official statistics - censuses, surveys, and administrative data projects
Sampling, weighting, data cleaning, and analysis
